HI folks, we publish an Ushahidi weekly report on the wiki. I&#39;ve taken to cross posting it to share updates.<br><br><a href="http://wiki.ushahidi.com/display/WIKI/Ushahidi+Weekly+-+6">This week&#39;s Report</a><br clear="all">

<br>Manu and his team did a fantastic job of using the hashtag #thefuturewewant to map out what people think about the Rio+20 conference, sustainability, environmental issues and more. Take a look at <a href="http://www.ourrio20.com/">OurRio20</a>. He could use a hand on this project.<br>

<br>Some things to help out:<br><ul><li>Can you help provide some thoughts on election and security issues? <a href="https://docs.google.com/a/ushahidi.com/document/d/17lotKwz2TbpaiUv5-ka3ZA8Ees2VPbEtQZBwybYMU70/edit">I will share with credit in my talk. </a></li>

<li>We are having some fun trying to build localization better for translators? Can you provide feedback into what we can do to<a href="http://wiki.ushahidi.com/display/WIKI/Localization+and+Translation"> improve translation?</a><br>

</li></ul><br>Anyone can add their thoughts, needs and updates to the weekly report. <a href="http://wiki.ushahidi.com/display/WIKI/Ushahidi+Weekly+-+7">Click here get started for next week.</a><br><br>I&#39;ve collected a list of amazing deployments found this week. Any feedback on who should be the <a href="http://wiki.ushahidi.com/display/WIKI/Deployments+of+the+Week">Deployment of the Week?</a><br>

